OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying damp
OL,6,Ffor some this evening with patchy rain
OL,7,Fand drizzle. This increasingly
OL,8,Fconfined to higher ground overnight
OL,9,Fand turning dry for many. Remaining
OL,10,Fmurky in some coastal regions with
OL,11,Fmist and hill fog possible. Staying
OL,12,Fbreezy on coasts. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FLargely cloudy on Friday with
OL,15,Foccasional light drizzle, mainly over
OL,16,Fthe moors. Brightening up in places
OL,17,Fwith sunnier spells developing in the
OL,18,Feast during the afternoon. Feeling
OL,19,Fwarmer than recently.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
